description: This file initializes the React application by rendering the <App /> component into the DOM element with id 'root'. It also imports necessary dependencies including React, ReactDOM, a CSS stylesheet, and the main App component.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root to manage and render a React application into a specific DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React components into the root DOM node.
